{"tid":166752,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你是誰的新歡和舊愛🎵","createTime":"2017-03-22T11:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T15:57:58.000Z","uid":42568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7df8dab34ce3cf23581f18978c24d38463fa9a4","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:07:06.000Z","msg":"再見舊情人<br />\n<br />\n我是時間的新歡"},{"pid":"0d6cd4e8be78d3b9939d803e2abf641f15dd73a5","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"想把世界的雨都淋個遍<br />\n<br />\n當我獨自躲在大雨的屋簷<br />\n<br />\n遠光燈的那一邊<br />\n<br />\n會不會有一個晴朗的天"},{"pid":"dbe527fe9ba6ec20cfa4449e19f89a16319ab02e","tid":166752,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"再見"},{"pid":"d459beb01dd590a732472195348e7fec644e4f6e","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再見</blockquote><br />\n當你離開了夢中<br />\n<br />\n天地萬物都失聰<br />\n<br />\n追不上飛馳的鐘<br />\n<br />\n捉不住跑路的蟲"},{"pid":"c40629632d0607d9605dab26ddbeac2532f2dfa7","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:36:00.000Z","msg":"在人間 有誰活著不像是一場煉獄<br />\n<br />\n我不哭我已經沒有尊嚴能放棄"},{"pid":"be785a290c720729ee27999359201fc30a0bf41b","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T02:22:04.000Z","msg":"你是旅途　你是故鄉"},{"pid":"c953ad2a31b2619cf6cce406a1b242d43e92d0ca","tid":166752,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"再見 我的初戀～"},{"pid":"f966763c4cbf5a424e3f2eee4b8c93adfe94762e","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再見 我的初戀～</blockquote><br />\n八十歲的某一天<br />\n<br />\n我能否再想起你的臉"},{"pid":"6b37cf4eb4b30c0dfa0a8fae113dbfa78c75b276","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"是否參禪人未曾言笑   <br />\n<br />\n望世人看破塵囂<br />\n<br />\n我甘心困你掌心無處可逃    <br />\n<br />\n無處落腳"},{"pid":"b57c48e5559973ef2854e697bd113fc372a2d4d3","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"其實你我都一樣 終將被遺忘 郭源潮<br />\n<br />\n你的病也和我的一樣<br />\n<br />\n風月難扯 離合不騷<br />\n<br />\n層樓終究誤少年 自由早晚亂余生"},{"pid":"7739b991707b59c648a7614eacb2f32746bc9e69","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:06:24.000Z","msg":"我曾不知疲倦　安靜的等妳回來<br />\n<br />\n沒有煩心的夢　沒有瑣碎的一切"},{"pid":"0ccd4bd9164407ac274c3b0fcdb21360034495b2","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:33:03.000Z","msg":"你曾經做的那個征服世界的夢<br />\n<br />\n就像個玩笑深藏在你記憶之中<br />\n<br />\n生活在檢驗著你到底 是龍還是蟲"},{"pid":"55d2685a3cbf37d723a8931848a15bf9fb70ffd3","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"兩顆心 離散 兩端<br />\n<br />\n風一吹就散<br />\n<br />\n開始不安 慌亂<br />\n<br />\n沒了明與暗<br />\n<br />\n我只能承受 孤單<br />\n<br />\n將與暗作伴<br />\n<br />\n習慣漂流 聚散 悲歡。"},{"pid":"ac27aefabf3966e64cfc83f6e5addc0b42353b7f","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:22:40.000Z","msg":"理想今年你幾歲<br />\n<br />\n你總是誘惑著年輕的朋友<br />\n<br />\n你總是謝了又開給我驚喜<br />\n<br />\n又讓我沉入失望的生活裡"},{"pid":"0b9ca588bfa92dd2a55a40b3193885796be46a04","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"別看我瘋言亂語笑聲有多美<br />\n<br />\n轉過頭不願你見我落幾行淚"},{"pid":"52807f1ff587e0dacca3bba253e33fb9d9f93c11","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:47:07.000Z","msg":"我還在一天一天守候<br />\n<br />\n夢中伸出雙手<br />\n<br />\n迎著那暖暖春風"},{"pid":"136876469a204ede77fd3037f30834ea3716a11a","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"冬天她走了 冬天又來了<br />\n<br />\n這循環的季節<br />\n<br />\n多像我們循環播放的生活"},{"pid":"deebb9f04c4d2a41b94872b10457d50542e9ad76","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"別讓等不了的擁抱 停止了你的尋找 <br />\n<br />\n你可知道這世界有多想要"},{"pid":"ec7e843ed0fe91a3f140cc95d5523d5f7e58fa82","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"今夕是何夕<br />\n<br />\n當來不及傳遞的鐘聲響起<br />\n<br />\n於是我們都發現了歲月的意義"},{"pid":"adeba68239610f1600cdb659e52f6a069facaf7c","tid":166752,"uid":42568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"陪我到可可西裡看一看海<br />\n<br />\n不要未來 只要你來"}]}